    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper<strong> </strong>and shred</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
