    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once very hot, add your <strong>meat-free mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!) and cook for 7-8 min or until browned, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Once browned, add your <strong>ground cumin</strong> and and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 2 min further – this is your <strong>spiced meat-free mince</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
