    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil half a kettle</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> natural yoghurt</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>chipotle yoghurt</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
