    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the<strong> spiced meat-free mince</strong> to a plate and set aside</p><p>Drain and rinse your<strong> black beans</strong></p><p>Return the pan (and any oil) to a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>drained black beans</strong>, your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant – these are your <strong>smoky beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
