    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 150ml<span class=\"text-purple\"><span class=\"text-danger\"> [195ml] </span>[250ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> vegetable stock</strong> and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<strong> lime[s] </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for 3-4 min further</p><p>Remove the <strong>smoky</strong> <strong>beans</strong> from the heat and mash into a semi-smooth paste – these are your <strong>refried smoky beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
