    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the juice of the <strong>remaining lime[s]</strong> with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> shredded lettuce </strong>and<strong> diced tomato </strong>and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p>",
