    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble your burrito bowl, top the <strong>cooked rice </strong>with the<strong> spiced meat-free mince</strong> and serve the<strong> chopped salad </strong>and <strong>refried smoky beans</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>chipotle yoghurt</strong>,<strong> </strong>sprinkle with the <strong>grated cheese </strong>and garnish with the<strong> chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
